      <pubDate>Mon, 30 Dec 2024 08:22:08 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>欧洲央行行长表示贸易战可能将中国通货紧缩输出至欧洲</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-30/ecb-s-knot-says-trade-war-could-export-china-deflation-to-europe</link>
      <description><![CDATA[欧洲央行管理委员会委员克拉斯·诺特表示，如果美国通过征收新的关税引发贸易战，中国可能开始以折扣价向欧洲出售产品。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-30/ecb-s-knot-says-trade-war-could-export-china-deflation-to-europe</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 30 Dec 2024 08:10:52 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>西班牙通胀加速，支持欧洲央行逐步降息</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-30/spanish-inflation-accelerates-backing-gradual-ecb-rate-cuts</link>
      <description><![CDATA[西班牙通胀率本月升幅超出预期，受基数效应影响，通胀率连续第二个月维持在 2% 以上，这为逐步降息提供了依据。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-30/spanish-inflation-accelerates-backing-gradual-ecb-rate-cuts</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 30 Dec 2024 08:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>卢比波动率飙升，印度储备银行的货币策略成为焦点</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-30/rupee-volatility-surge-puts-rbi-s-currency-strategy-in-focus</link>
      <description><![CDATA[随着美元走强，人们越来越猜测印度央行可能会放松对印度卢比的严格控制，印度卢比波动率的指标跃升至一年多来的最高水平。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-30/rupee-volatility-surge-puts-rbi-s-currency-strategy-in-focus</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 30 Dec 2024 06:42:01 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
